{
  "stem": "1857.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 290.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a marshal, Rydz-Smigly, and there was a prime minister who was very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So on the level of the government and on our standing in Poland, we didn't feel secure since 1935.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time my father was talking about it, but never was the proper time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We talked about it at the-- the dinner table and with friends-- I remember when people used to come to the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was never a proper-- not yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In another year.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Another.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let the children get education first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let's do this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let's do that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He-- he-- he did want to leave for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the war out, there was tremendous change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was-- the school was closed in December of 1939.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans walked in September 5, 1939 in the city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the Germans walked in, we were standing on the streets watching the German Army marching in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never expected-- well, we knew of Nazi anti-Jewish laws, but we never expected of the extreme happenings, what would happen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if we would have known it, by the way, we-- we-- we would have probably left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father, a few days before the war started, Kaminski owned a big factory of bicycles, which factory was in Warsaw, sent a truck for us to bring us to Warsaw, because we felt that Krakow will be occupied in no time, because Krakow was close to the German and Austrian borders.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, Warsaw will hold off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So Kaminski sent a truck for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were all packed, sitting on the valises, waiting for the truck to come and take us to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
